  "technicalDetails": "PPT (PowerPoint Binary File Format) is an OLE2 Compound File Binary. The PowerPoint Document stream contains a sequence of PowerPoint records starting with a CurrentUserAtom at offset 0. Each record has a 4-byte header (version/type nibbles) + 4-byte length. Slide records (SlideAtom) reference MasterAtom for layout templates.",
  "completenessScore": 82
}



